Invocation Name: parent facts
des:
A silly collection of facts no one ever told you about being a parent. Have you ever stepped on a lego? Has your child ever had a meltdown because you asked them to wear pants? Simply say "Open Parent Facts" to get a little comic relief from this crazy, exhausting, amazing journey called parenthood.
